{"tid":111093,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[日航體驗]安安全全正正常常保命MK子東京之旅","createTime":"2017-02-07T07:33:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T06:20:55.000Z","uid":81211,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"826d0331be7e3f8b48cfe510f1e093166f293cd6","tid":111093,"uid":81211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:33:00.000Z","msg":"尋晚係電影中心等緊LA LA LAND開埸，又沒咩做，決定寫番篇遊記讚下Japan Airline(JAL)。<br />\n<br />\n但最近旅遊台好似變左新假期咁，去下日本又玩命，旅行十日又痴線，坐下火車又極邪惡，所以我決定學新假期，整番個極邪惡紫薯芝士系列，集合曬大家夢想。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B8cC42Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB8cC42Y.jpg&h=93c35a2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n番正題:<br />\n年廿八番番下工，突然比文員仔話我AL太多，一定要我年廿九放假去清假，上網查下又見到JAL聽日仲有里數飛剩，諗左一分鐘就決定換飛，放工番屋企執行李，同訂酒店，就踏上這埸無盡之旅(真係諗起都覺得文青，其實只係去左四日)。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4J67jC7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4J67jC7.jpg&h=3481b49e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v8MU8L4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv8MU8L4.jpg&h=ff49da49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去程坐Boeing 777-200。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CVGvBV2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCVGvBV2.jpg&h=cf8af3f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n部機似重新裝修過，座位感覺好坐過CX，但如果講電影種類都係比唔上Emirate Airline，事實我亦都係未坐過一間航空公司係多戲睇過Emirate。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8735p4S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8735p4S.jpg&h=d38ce6e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果講野飲種類，Singapore Airline其實多過Japan Airline，但JAL佢有一個優點，佢會印曬成個LIST出來俾你睇同簡(果個SkyTime - Kiwi好難飲，千奇唔好試)。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L3M305i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL3M305i.jpg&h=58f474d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n空姐年紀都係比較老，如果講空姐最正，首選xiāng găng airline，果種MK妹味真係不得了，但日航空姐服務同笑容真係好足，就算係香港藉空姐，都會感受到佢笑容，唔係CX空姐果種皮笑肉不笑或者西口西面(都市傳聞:如果用英文同CX空姐對答會好D)。<br />\n<br />\n但服務我果位日藉空姐英文水平就真係麻麻了，但點都好過xiāng găng airline。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qKOvdH1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqKOvdH1.jpg&h=d8db2e24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n細過屋企窮，未坐過飛機，大過之後，總係好想搵番依種童真，所以我有得簡，都會盡量叫兒童餐，拎飛行玩具。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/up86aqX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fup86aqX.jpg&h=0c42847a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以前睇到ANA個兒童餐真係充滿期待，點解可以靚到咁。<br />\n<br />\n但經過多年麥當當既黑椒漢堡訓練，我知道理想同現實往往係不符。<br />\n<br />\n香港去程個兒童餐，就算係Cathay Pacific同xiāng găng airline，我都會形容係童年陰影，狗都唔屌。<br />\n<br />\nJAL:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Gr6Yg9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Gr6Yg9.jpg&h=d1b9f012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCX:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6fNKdy6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6fNKdy6.jpg&h=4329cf62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幸好回程個兒童餐真係滿足到我夢想，食個兒童餐，都覺得做日本小朋友幸福過香港小朋友好多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ox69p38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fox69p38.jpg&h=70eef7d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開頭上餐果時，港藉空姐仲好疑惑係咪派錯餐俾我，因為前面兩個小朋友都沒叫兒童餐，但竟然後面個中年麻甩佬叫左兒童餐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5s4LL44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5s4LL44.jpg&h=4054236f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但同佢解釋完之後，佢不但沒恥笑我，仲好細心同我解釋每碟菜入面有咩食材，收完餐，問佢拿威士忌果陣，仲同我研究左陣ANA，JAL，CX，HX邊個兒童餐最得意。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0W3dx4R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0W3dx4R.jpg&h=886b6002&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有玩具玩，開心豬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4A7WCUs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4A7WCUs.jpg&h=d97c0e9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食完飛機餐之後，另外一位日藉空姐邀請左我去工作間，跟住拿左三款玩具俾我簡，有飛機模型，有筆盒，仲有個唔記得左係咩了，跟住仲問我個餐好唔好食。<br />\n<br />\n總結：成程機都好開心，期待下次再搭。"},{"pid":"e184bc56e9a47ee0fcac421dfa742755efda0c58","tid":111093,"uid":81211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:34:20.000Z","msg":"終於找左一篇遊記數，希望有機會可以寫埋科索沃篇遊記。"},{"pid":"8a34b82b08c3a369567922d2fb8cef2e848dce86","tid":111093,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:46:13.000Z","msg":"回程係日本上食物真係正好多<br />\n<br />\n原來有得叫兒童餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d718ddb6ba343bd9a9fd92709a90324136f84213","tid":111093,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:49:07.000Z","msg":"JAL同CX兒童餐入便D野好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483f7072e0818a8c336cd5ea24049ddf1dd14b2c","tid":111093,"uid":7778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:49:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>回程係日本上食物真係正好多<br />\n<br />\n原來有得叫兒童餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上機前book定<br />\n最遲係起飛前廿四小時"},{"pid":"98ddad78a0d45064cd587b2281408fcced036495","tid":111093,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:52:37.000Z","msg":"每次見人叫兒童餐就諗起以前有個POST, 有個阿叔周圍屌鳩人改特別餐"},{"pid":"a58b476d5ac2eabaeafedfc41d72e7c2ac767c7c","tid":111093,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:54:15.000Z","msg":"ana jal 機倉個感覺係乾淨過 cx 好多，cx 好撚霉。"},{"pid":"841046f1140751cd839485176a9562839b336531","tid":111093,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:59:44.000Z","msg":"架玩具飛機正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccd504dae37c118a18a07b023e0db056234ab49e","tid":111093,"uid":81211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:27:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>架玩具飛機正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宜家放左係台頭"},{"pid":"0bac1a67bc9733f83