al/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689219d2960ead37b398ffdc545c7d736293f846","tid":111093,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T10:24:18.000Z","msg":"jal空姐樣一時時 有d好撚靚 有d一般 但服務真心好 <br />\n機坐兩架比華航舊 有部tv壞左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4288aea9c8451a287fc4f02ffc1a1c7624199451","tid":111093,"uid":7778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T10:37:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去程同回程個餐差咁遠，一眼就分到個餐邊度上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nANA去程同回程都係差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d794a97b57c504609bb6de431066cdf4e6d08a","tid":111093,"uid":81211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T10:52:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪叫兒童就會有飛機送架喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，但要主動問"},{"pid":"7d6577fb7b2277cc12093d02cc238437fc16e506","tid":111093,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T11:33:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fcdbde614e838a67ad83bf97def29d0d861eb1a","tid":111093,"uid":81211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:27:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去程同回程個餐差咁遠，一眼就分到個餐邊度上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nANA去程同回程都係差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未有機會坐ANA"},{"pid":"609c51bc64c640a3ed38a7a2099036acdddd9c13","tid":111093,"uid":45928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:38:16.000Z","msg":"淨係飛機依 part 都咁精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b608cd0a7c14c8829a6393bb5e85ba51d7924e8","tid":111093,"uid":51028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-